To use API:

GET: backend.php?request=endpoint/verb/arg0/arg1/arg2/argN

example: backend.php?request=getblog/get/1
example: backend.php?request=getblog/get/*

POST: backend.php 
for parameters, use:

{ "request": "endpoint/verb/arg0/arg1/arg2/argN" }

The API returns data as JSON which is easy to parse in JavaScript. 
Use JS to populate the UI with the data you've requested using AJAX.


